commit.message:
Remove set_default_param_value from documentation.

2019-11-12  Martin Liska  <mliska@suse.cz>

	* common/common-target.def:
	Do not mention set_default_param_value
	and set_param_value.
	* doc/tm.texi: Likewise.

From-SVN: r278088
